snippet.title: This Southern Girl Can
snippet.description:
Hey, y'all! Welcome to my YouTube channel where you'll find loads of recipes, DIYs, and craft tutorials. Grab a glass of tea (the sweeter, the better), kick off your shoes, and stay a bit.

Business email: ThisSouthernGirlCan@gmail.com
This email is to only be used for business purposes. (Sponsorships, affiliates, paid promotions, etc.)If you have questions regarding crafting projects, contact me on Facebook or Instagram.

Mailing Address:
PO Box 1289
Lenoir, NC 28645

I do not live in the same town as my mailing address. I live an hour away. However, I do check this address once a week.
